title: Three Chain Links - Swell
description:
1. Look how bright the city burns at night... (Ambient mix of City Night by Peazy86)
2. I will always be with you Amy. (Ambient mix of Amy, I love you by Cloudkicker)
3. We're almost out! Hang on! (Ambient mix of Ophelia by Smiletron)
4. Go, be huge. (Ambient mix of Let Yourself Be Huge by Cloudkicker)
5. Roar, lion man, roar. (Ambient mix of Little Lion Man by Mumford and Sons)
6. Drone.
7. Prisoners no more. (Ambient mix of Level 1 POW Camp from POW - Prisoners Of War)
8. It's best not to tempt time. (Ambient mix of Tempting Time by Animals As Leaders)
9. Listen closely, I'm only going to say this once.
10. Keep formation, Metal Squad is approaching. (Ambient mix of Metal Squad from Thunder Force IV)

This is an album of ambient/noise/drone music inspired by the music from Dr3dd. 
If you payed for this you got ripped off! I will always give my music away for free or make it pay-what-you-want! Thanks for listening! 

If you liked this album, check out my blog at http://threechainlinks.tumblr.com/
where I post pixel art from video games as well as my own art and music.
